results.name: List of positive integers, ordered by asymptotic frequency of appearance in A003557; ties broken by listing smaller numbers first.
comment: A permutation of the natural numbers.
The natural density of positive integers m such that A003557(m) = a(n) equals 6/(A181798(n)*Pi^2). If m is coprime to 6, 3m and 4m appear in A003557 equally often.
formula: The natural density of positive integers m such that A003557(m) = n equals 6/(A181797(n)*Pi^2). A181797(n) = n*A048250(n).
results.author: _Matthew Vandermast_, Dec 05 2010
